<h3 class="aos-DS57-H3 aos-FL100 aos-MBM">The Buyer's Guides</h3><div id="aos-de-ti3039" class="aos-FL100 aos-DF aos-TAC"><span class="aos-de-ti-image aos-DF aos-TAC"><img class="aos-MW100" src="https://drsw10gc90t0z.cloudfront.net/AcuCustom/Sitename/Icon/Icons/BS-Buyers-Guides-720-x-405.png" alt="" title="" loading="lazy" /></span><div class="aos-de-ti-text aos-MTS"><div class="aos-DS57-WYSEdit"> <p>The Bookseller Buyer's Guides are published twice per year and contain comprehensive publisher and title info for thousands of titles due out in the next 6 months. With seasonal highlights and bestseller predictions from industry experts, there's a wealth of information to help you plan your buying and save you time.<br /><br />Each edition consists of three volumes: Fiction Buyer&#8217;s Guide, Non-Fiction Buyer&#8217;s Guide and Children&#8217;s Buyer&#8217;s Guide.<br /><br /><a class="aos-WYSEdit-button" href="https://thebookseller.affino.com/subscription-products/buyers-guides-annual-subscription">Buy Now</a></p> </div></div></div>
</div>
